card.text:
Ward {1}
Convert ({T}: Target creature you control switches its power and toughness until end of turn.)
Whenever Convert becomes tapped, creatures you control gain vigilance until end of turn.

Equipped creature gets +1/+0 and has lifelink and deathtouch.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, you may return target permanent card with mana value 2 or less from your graveyard to your hand.
Equip {1}{W}{B}

Equipped creature has +1/+1 and flying.
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, you may return target instant or sorcery card with mana value 2 or less from your graveyard to your hand.
Equip {1}{U}{U}

Ward {1}
Dismembered Leviathan enters with a trample counter on it if it was cast.
Whenever Dismembered Leviathan attacks, tap target creature an opponent controls and put a stun counter on it.

Equipped creature gets +2/+2 and has "Ward—Pay 2 life."
Whenever equipped creature deals combat damage to a player, that player reveals their hand. You choose a nonland card from it. That player discards that card.
Equip {3}

Equipped creature has +2/+2 and reach.
Whenever equipped creature attacks, if its power is 5 or greater, you gain 2 life and draw a card.
Equip {3}

